#include <iostream>
using namespace std;
#define ll long long

int main()
{   ll t;
    cin>>t;
    while(t--)
    {   ll x,p,m=0,z[1002]={0};
        cin>>x;
        for(ll i=0;i<x;++i)
        {   cin>>p;
            if(p>m)
                m=p;
            ++z[p];
        }
        ll k=0;
        for(ll i=1;i<=m;++i)
            if(z[i]>1)
            {   cout<<"NO\n";
                k=1;
                break;
            }  
        if(k==0)
            cout<<"YES\n";
    }
    return 0;
}
